message: "If you use project-starter in your work, please cite it as below."
title: "project-starter"
abstract: >-
  Day-1 scaffolding for AI agent projects. Templates and tooling that produce
  consistent project structure, persistent agent memory, design discipline,
  and skill recommendations. Primary target is Claude Code; the portable
  subset (skills, scaffolder, memory hierarchy, contracts) works with any
  Agent Skills-compatible client (Cursor, Gemini CLI, OpenCode, Junie, Goose,
  Amp, and others). Authored by Liz Osborn.
type: software
